{"tid":714735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"學術開放環境遭利用 美國防部調查與贏國合作大學","createTime":"2018-06-23T23:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T10:15:15.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c05fc17de395942f16c04fcceb08f52db9af57","tid":714735,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"學術開放環境遭利用 美國防部調查與中國合作大學<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2466815\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2466815&d=HcadlA1bA2XoVPK3oCgCFLZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=752e81f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2466815&h=9430043f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2466815</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國與中國關係漸趨緊張，外媒報導，美國防部官員透露，美國防部正在審查同時與國防部和中國企業合作的美國大學。<br />\n<br />\n《美國之音》報導，美國防部製造與工業政策事務副助理部長丘寧（Eric Chewning）表示，中國企業利用美國開放的學術環境與創新模式，進入模式內部，但卻保持自身的封閉性，因此國防部啟動對美國大學的審查。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，美國防部研究與工業事務副部長葛瑞芬（Michael Griffin）表示，對於與中國企業在敏感技術領域有所合作的美國大學，國防部不應與其有聯繫。他提醒，目前有超過3萬名的中國學生，在美國大學攻讀科技、工程等博士學位，各部門需要為國家風險重新評估。"},{"pid":"680a0b22f2fd713b1ad083f03d6130cee4920fd1","tid":714735,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:16:23.000Z","msg":"如果唔係上次中情局死咁多人，應該一早就查到<br />\n不過而家都唔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24343e928a85ed20b842e7be8e9967cb2d1edf0d","tid":714735,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3348f6aab90d9b5e3536917eb84a9f20c6eea7e4","tid":714735,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680a0b22f2fd713b1ad083f03d6130cee4920fd1","tid":714735,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T00:16:23.000Z","msg":"如果唔係上次中情局死咁多人，應該一